{"tid":1807034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日咁快就腰斬， 係因為我地摸索到黃圈>工會>獨立呢條方程式， 支共嚇撚到瀨屎","createTime":"2020-01-01T15:25:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T16:03:57.000Z","uid":57205,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"bc7a66a62d7fa39b89ec9e12d4c5a09966c4e97a","tid":1807034,"uid":57205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:25:23.000Z","msg":"黃色經濟圈&gt;&gt;壯大同路人勢力，有助建立工會<br />\n工會&gt;&gt;參見波蘭團結工會，最終波蘭共產黨倒台<br />\n去到最後，香港獨立不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家終於開始探索到呢條成功方程式<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支共仲唔瀨哂屎咁腰斬"},{"pid":"ebe9604e872fb357ae38ffb18d8d09416646e2ea","tid":1807034,"uid":34780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:28:53.000Z","msg":"推 <br />\n經過今日好撚肯定佢地好驚黃圈同工會<br />\n敵人反對的 敵人恐懼的<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93ea0cebb3386fff76f380c095728dfdd38b53e1","tid":1807034,"uid":243677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:29:59.000Z","msg":"入工會 繼續壯大黃圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a85b6fb8f16cc33bd071c2d96a98febecdb4d136","tid":1807034,"uid":59297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:30:01.000Z","msg":"港獨思潮<br />\n黃色經濟圈<br />\n組織工會<br />\n<br />\n呢三者將會係我地2020嘅抗爭目標，三者缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" 